author: mirichmo
body:
[PerformWSManPluginReportCompletion](https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/blob/b3940fe15babae000dc6ee4f31bebf3f6a843a3b/src/powershell-native/nativemsh/pwrshplugin/pwrshplugin.h#L1095) is dead code that is no longer used. It should have been removed during the purge of the workflow code and is safe to remove.

The [corresponding entry in pwrshplugin.def](https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/blob/b3940fe15babae000dc6ee4f31bebf3f6a843a3b/src/powershell-native/nativemsh/pwrshplugin/pwrshplugin.def#L18) should also be removed as well.

### Version Info
-------------------------
6.0.0-beta.9
title: Remove PerformWSManPluginReportCompletion from pwrshplugin.dll
